Let's face it: the struggle is all too real when it comes to getting noticed as an independent young artist. Everybody is a rapper these days, it seems, and these 10 artists are only a tiny percentage of rappers taking to Instagram, trying to get noticed by successful rappers.

Do they really think that anyone is going to check the comments section, go through the hundreds of comments on a Drake photo, and click the stupid link to a random SoundCloud in your Instagram bio? Being the good samaritans we are here at Pigeons, we took it upon ourselves to check out some of these tracks that the famous artists likely never will.

Here's what we discovered, and some of it is NSFE (not safe for ears).
